<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Grid Bot - Announcements</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0f172a;
            --surface-color: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.7);
            --accent-color: #f97316;
            --glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --text-main: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
            --success: #22c55e;
            --danger: #ef4444;
            --twitch: #9146FF;
            --youtube: #FF0000;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.1), transparent 40%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 90% 80%, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1), transparent 40%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: var(--text-main);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .navbar {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            padding: 16px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-brand { font-weight: 800; font-size: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
        .nav-brand span { color: var(--accent-color); }

        .btn {
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .btn-secondary { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); color: white; border: 1px solid var(--glass-border); }
        .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); }
        .btn-primary { background: var(--accent-color); color: white; }
        .btn-primary:hover { background: #ea580c; }
        .btn-danger { background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1); color: var(--danger); border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2); padding: 4px 10px; font-size: 12px; }
        .btn-danger:hover { background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2); }

        .main-content {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .header { margin-bottom: 32px; }
        .header h1 { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .header p { color: var(--text-muted); }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .panel {
            background: var(--surface-color);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .panel-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 16px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
        }

        .panel-header h2 { font-size: 20px; }
        
        .twitch-icon { color: var(--twitch); font-size: 24px; }
        .youtube-icon { color: var(--youtube); font-size: 24px; }

        .list-group { margin-bottom: 24px; }
        .list-item {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .empty-state { color: var(--text-muted); font-style: italic; font-size: 14px; }

        .add-form {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        .add-form input {
            flex: 1;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            color: white;
            font-family: inherit;
        }
        .add-form input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--accent-color); }

        footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 13px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            margin-top: auto;
        }
        .made-by { font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent-color); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-brand">
            🫵 the <span>grid.</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-secondary">Zurück zum Dashboard</a>
    </nav>

    <main class="main-content">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>📢 Announcements System</h1>
            <p>Verwalte die Twitch-Streamer und YouTube-Kanäle, die automatisch in Kanal <code>1338098698042736711</code> angekündigt werden sollen.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid">
            <!-- TWITCH -->
            <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-header">
                    <span class="twitch-icon">🟪</span>
                    <h2>Twitch Livestreams</h2>
                </div>
                
                <div class="list-group">
                    <% if (config.twitch.length === 0) { %>
                        <div class="empty-state">Keine Twitch-Streamer eingetragen.</div>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <% config.twitch.forEach(function(username) { %>
                            <div class="list-item">
                                <span><%= username %></span>
                                <form action="/dashboard/announcements/remove" method="POST" style="margin:0;">
                                    <input type="hidden" name="type" value="twitch">
                                    <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= username %>">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">Löschen</button>
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        <% }); %>
                    <% } %>
                </div>

                <form action="/dashboard/announcements/add" method="POST" class="add-form">
                    <input type="hidden" name="type" value="twitch">
                    <input type="text" name="id" placeholder="Twitch Benutzername (z.B. montanablack)" required>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Hinzufügen</button>
                </form>
            </div>

            <!-- YOUTUBE -->
            <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-header">
                    <span class="youtube-icon">🟥</span>
                    <h2>YouTube Videos</h2>
                </div>
                
                <div class="list-group">
                    <% if (config.youtube.length === 0) { %>
                        <div class="empty-state">Keine YouTube-Kanäle eingetragen.</div>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <% config.youtube.forEach(function(channelId) { %>
                            <div class="list-item">
                                <span style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px;"><%= channelId %></span>
                                <form action="/dashboard/announcements/remove" method="POST" style="margin:0;">
                                    <input type="hidden" name="type" value="youtube">
                                    <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= channelId %>">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">Löschen</button>
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        <% }); %>
                    <% } %>
                </div>

                <form action="/dashboard/announcements/add" method="POST" class="add-form">
                    <input type="hidden" name="type" value="youtube">
                    <input type="text" name="id" placeholder="YouTube Channel ID (z.B. UC...)" required>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Hinzufügen</button>
                </form>
                <p style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 8px;">Achtung: Bitte die genaue <b>Channel ID</b> eintragen (beginnt meistens mit UC). Nicht das @Handle!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        made by <span class="made-by">MaxiFaxiPaxi</span>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
